  "notes": [
    "This case report describes a complex genetic evaluation of a young woman with breast cancer who was found to have a mosaic TP53 variant diagnostic for Li-Fraumeni syndrome.",
    "The case highlights the importance of distinguishing between germline, mosaic, and clonal hematopoiesis origins of TP53 variants for appropriate clinical management.",
    "Multiple tissue testing and embryo analysis were used to confirm the mosaic nature of the TP53 variant."
  ]
